parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunction of the hybrid powertrain can cause the vehicle to lose power, slow down, or stall, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The vehicle slows down or loses power
the vehicle is unable to accelerate
the vehicle is stuck in a high-rev
the vehicle is unable to climb hills or maintain speed.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunction of the brake system can cause the vehicle to lose braking power, leading to accidents or injuries.
symptoms: The brake system error light illuminates
the vehicle slows down or loses braking power

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the fuel pump can cause the vehicle to stall, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Loss of Engine Power and Acceleration
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The loss of engine power and acceleration can cause accidents or leave the driver stranded, especially when driving on highways.
symptoms: sudden loss of power while driving.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The inaccurate vehicle range calculation can cause drivers to run out of gas in remote areas, leading to dangerous situations.
symptoms: range estimate shows off even when fuel level is very low

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the infotainment system can cause the rear-view camera and blind-spot monitor to malfunction, leading to potential accidents and safety risks.
symptoms: The infotainment system is slow and buggy
causing the rear-view camera to freeze or not display at all
and the blind-spot monitor to malfunction.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the clutch and transmission can cause the vehicle to lose power and accelerate unexpectedly, leading to potential accidents and safety risks.
symptoms: often when the battery is low and on slight inclines.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the sensor and warning systems can cause multiple warning indicators to illuminate on the instrument panel, leading to confusion and potential safety risks.
symptoms: Multiple warning indicators illuminate on the instrument panel
and road departure mitigation system problems.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the charging system can cause the vehicle to not start or drive, leading to inconvenience and potential safety risks.
symptoms: The vehicle's onboard charger shuts off when sensing the charging station's energy management controller
causing a "total system failure" warning and preventing the vehicle from starting or driving.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The unusual noises and clicking sounds can be distracting and cause concern for the driver, potentially leading to accidents or safety risks.
symptoms: A loud clicking sound is heard from the dashboard
which does not go away even when the car is turned off.
